ers.home.com/sbugelli/rockwalk.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Is it actually possible?</span><hr size=1> For an enchanter to solo pre 50+? Well I don't mean solo as in killing that annoying puma that broke your med. I mean solo as for exp. If anyone knows of a way a 35 enchanter to do so, can you tell me how?!?! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
